{"type":"message","id":"8b135fec","parentId":"92fd8c0b","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:23:28.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so there's:\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-selector` - which seems to be a proper workspace in the main workspace dir\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts` - also in the main workspace dir\n- `~/workspace-tts` - in HOME dir\n\nThe backup script has:\n- `do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\"` → targets `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/` which doesn't exist (should be `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts/` or `~/workspace-tts/`)\n\n\n- `do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"` - this backs up the entire workspace directory, so it's already capturing workspace-selector and workspace-tts\n- There's no backup for `~/workspace-tts` either, which is where the actual content lives\n- The user's earlier message suggests they thought tts had already replaced selector, so maybe these directories are duplicates or one replaced the other\n\nThe real problem is that `workspace-tts` exists in two places: `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts` gets backed up by the workspace rsync, but `~/workspace-tts` doesn't, while the script tries to back up `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts` which doesn't actually exist.\n","thinkingSignature":"876e36c3e986cbb3a530a43e558a1f8a9288e49d49c670fce079803dbcfd9679"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n明白了。你说的是 `selector` 改名成了 `tts`，但备份脚本里的路径是错的：\n\n- **脚本写的是** `$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/` = `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/` — 这个路径根本不存在\n- **实际 workspace 在** `~/workspace-tts/`（HOME 下）或者 `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts/`（workspace 主目录下的子文件夹）\n\n所以 backup 脚本里那行 `$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/` 一直是个死路径，从来没备份成功过。\n\n但好消息是：`do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\"` 会备份整个 workspace 目录，所以 `~/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-tts/` 其实是**被包含在 workspace 备份里的**。\n\n所以 `~/workspace-tts/` 才是真正缺失的（因为它是 HOME 下的独立 workspace，不在 workspace/ 子目录里）。\n\n要修复吗？把脚本里那个错误的 `workspace-tts` 行改成 `$HOME/workspace-tts/` 的 rsync 行就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":498,"cacheRead":66710,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67333,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780057386122,"responseId":"0668b82a7803e9348cccc94943c8b491"}}
