{"type":"message","id":"f22a7b0c","parentId":"1338bddb","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:24:47.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TK product selection agent (TK选品大师) says it's in the `/home/halei/workspace-tts` directory. So the backup script is wrong - it's trying to backup from `$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/` which is `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/` (doesn't exist), but the actual location is `~/workspace-tts/` (in HOME).\n\nI need to fix the backup script. The line:\n```bash\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\"\n```\n\nShould be:\n```bash\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\"\n```\n\nThis will correctly backup `~/workspace-tts/` to the backup repo.\n\n\nNow I'll apply this fix to the backup script.\n","thinkingSignature":"8df2c6dd5d8cc5f5394ad7647811d8cc9cf5b01651ee936782d889eb744b13f3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n那问题就清楚了。备份脚本写的是 `$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/`（即 `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/`），路径根本不对，实际 workspace 在 `~/workspace-tts/`。\n\n我来修复备份脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6qu82vx2xh73_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"do_rsync \"$HOME/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\"","oldText":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\""}],"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1365,"output":312,"cacheRead":65996,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780057477385,"responseId":"0668b886b236c4a25256688ed8d0f514"}}
